---
---

<section id="about" class="section about-section" aria-label="About Philip">
  <div class="container about-inner">

    <!-- Left: Bio -->
    <div class="about-text">
      <p class="section-label">🧠 About</p>
      <h2 class="section-title">Vision × AI × Real-world systems</h2>

      <div class="bio-paragraphs">
        <p>
          I'm a Doctor of Optometry and software engineer focused on assistive AI and computer vision.
          My clinical training at the University of Cape Coast Eye Clinic and Permeff Eye Care gave me
          direct experience with the full spectrum of ocular conditions — and a precise understanding
          of how visual impairment shapes real lives.
        </p>
        <p>
          That clinical lens shapes how I build technology. At <a href="https://www.ally.me" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Envision Technologies</a>,
          I work on Ally — an AI accessibility platform for over 100,000 blind and low vision users.
          The work demands that accessibility be infrastructure: reliable, fast, and unambiguous
          for users who have no visual fallback.
        </p>
        <p>
          My core research is Safe Step — an assistive navigation system combining obstacle detection,
          path segmentation, and voice feedback for independent outdoor navigation. The goal is
          real-world performance, not benchmark performance.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Right: Callout + Details -->
    <aside class="about-callout">
      <blockquote class="philosophy-quote">
        <p>Accessibility is not a feature.<br />It is infrastructure.</p>
        <footer>— Philip Abakah</footer>
      </blockquote>

      <div class="about-details">
        <div class="detail-row">
          <span class="detail-key">📍 Location</span>
          <span class="detail-val">Accra, Ghana</span>
        </div>
        <div class="detail-row">
          <span class="detail-key">🎓 Education</span>
          <span class="detail-val">Doctor of Optometry — UCC</span>
        </div>
        <div class="detail-row">
          <span class="detail-key">💼 Currently</span>
          <span class="detail-val">Software Engineer @ Envision</span>
        </div>
        <div class="detail-row">
          <span class="detail-key">🔬 Research</span>
          <span class="detail-val">Assistive nav, CV, glaucoma AI</span>
        </div>
        <div class="detail-row">
          <span class="detail-key">🎯 Interests</span>
          <span class="detail-val">F1, illustration, painting, cooking</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </aside>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about-section {
    background: var(--color-bg-secondary);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border-soft);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border-soft);
  }

  .about-inner {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 48px;
    align-items: start;
  }

  @media (min-width: 1024px) {
    .about-inner {
      grid-template-columns: 3fr 2fr;
      gap: 72px;
    }
  }

  .bio-paragraphs {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 18px;
  }

  .bio-paragraphs p {
    font-size: 15px;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .bio-paragraphs a {
    color: var(--color-accent);
    text-decoration: none;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(96, 165, 250, 0.3);
    transition: border-color 0.15s ease;
  }

  .bio-paragraphs a:hover { border-color: var(--color-accent); }

  /* Callout */
  .about-callout {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 24px;
  }

  .philosophy-quote {
    border-left: 2px solid var(--color-accent);
    padding-left: 18px;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .philosophy-quote p {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 17px;
    font-weight: 500;
    line-height: 1.55;
    color: var(--color-text);
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }

  .philosophy-quote footer {
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--color-text-mute);
  }

  /* Details card */
  .about-details {
    background: var(--color-bg-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border-soft);
    border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .detail-row {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 12px;
    padding: 12px 16px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border-soft);
  }

  .detail-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; }

  .detail-key {
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--color-text-tertiary);
    white-space: nowrap;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .detail-val {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    text-align: right;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }
</style>
